revisions.description: The initial revision of this MIB module.

h3cTransceiver.contactinfo: Platform Team Hangzhou H3C Tech. Co., Ltd. Hai-Dian District Beijing P.R. China http://www.h3c.com Zip:100085
h3cTransceiver.description: The objects in this MIB module are used to display the information of transceiver on interface.

h3cTransceiverInfoTable.name: h3cTransceiverInfoTable
h3cTransceiverInfoTable.description: This table show the information of transceiver on interface.

h3cTransceiverHardwareType.name: h3cTransceiverHardwareType
h3cTransceiverHardwareType.description: Hardware type of the interface, such as SM(single mode).

h3cTransceiverType.name: h3cTransceiverType
h3cTransceiverType.description: Type of the interface, such as SFP/XFP/GBIC.

h3cTransceiverWaveLength.name: h3cTransceiverWaveLength
h3cTransceiverWaveLength.description: Wave length of the interface, measured in nanometer.

h3cTransceiverFiberDiameterType.name: h3cTransceiverFiberDiameterType
h3cTransceiverFiberDiameterType.description: The diameter of the fiber, measured in micron. fiber9 - 9 micron multi-mode fiber fiber50 - 50 micron multi-mode fiber fiber625 - 62.5 micron multi-mode fiber copper - copper cable.

h3cTransceiverTransferDistance.name: h3cTransceiverTransferDistance
h3cTransceiverTransferDistance.description: The maximal distance which the interface could transmit, measured in meter.

h3cTransceiverDiagnostic.name: h3cTransceiverDiagnostic
h3cTransceiverDiagnostic.description: Indicating the digital diagnostic monitoring function .

h3cTransceiverCurTXPower.name: h3cTransceiverCurTXPower
h3cTransceiverCurTXPower.description: Indicating the current transmitted power . The unit is in hundredths of dBM.

h3cTransceiverMaxTXPower.name: h3cTransceiverMaxTXPower
h3cTransceiverMaxTXPower.description: Indicating the maximal transmitted power . The unit is in hundredths of dBM.

h3cTransceiverMinTXPower.name: h3cTransceiverMinTXPower
h3cTransceiverMinTXPower.description: Indicating the minimal transmitted power . The unit is in hundredths of dBM.

h3cTransceiverCurRXPower.name: h3cTransceiverCurRXPower
h3cTransceiverCurRXPower.description: Indicating the current received power . The unit is in hundredths of dBM.

h3cTransceiverMaxRXPower.name: h3cTransceiverMaxRXPower
h3cTransceiverMaxRXPower.description: Indicating the maximal received power . The unit is in hundredths of dBM.

h3cTransceiverMinRXPower.name: h3cTransceiverMinRXPower
h3cTransceiverMinRXPower.description: Indicating the minimal received power . The unit is in hundredths of dBM.

h3cTransceiverTemperature.name: h3cTransceiverTemperature
h3cTransceiverTemperature.description: Indicating the current temperature. The unit is celsius.

h3cTransceiverVoltage.name: h3cTransceiverVoltage
h3cTransceiverVoltage.description: Indicating the current voltage . The unit is in hundredths of V

h3cTransceiverBiasCurrent.name: h3cTransceiverBiasCurrent
h3cTransceiverBiasCurrent.description: Indicating the current bias electric current . The unit is in hundredths of mA
